flowchart TD
    ADMIN([Admin])
    COORD([Coordinator])
    STUDENT([Student])
    ACAD_SUP([Academic /<br/>Dept. Supervisor])
    IND_SUP([Industrial<br/>Supervisor])

    %% Admin interactions
    ADMIN -->|Creates / Manages| FAC_DEPT[Faculties &<br/>Departments]
    ADMIN -->|Invites| COORD
    ADMIN -->|Invites / Manages| ACAD_SUP
    ADMIN -->|Configures| SETTINGS[System Settings<br/>& Scoring Rules]
    ADMIN -->|Views| REPORTS[System Reports<br/>& Analytics]

    %% Coordinator interactions
    COORD -->|Invites / Manages| STUDENT
    COORD -->|Invites / Manages| ACAD_SUP
    COORD -->|Assigns| IND_SUP
    COORD -->|Approves| STD_PLACEMENT[Student Placement]
    COORD -->|Approves| COMPLIANCE[Compliance Forms]
    COORD -->|Approves| TECH_REPORT[Final Tech Reports]
    COORD -->|Oversees| VISITS[Supervisor Visits]
    COORD -->|Views| DEPT_REPORTS[Department Analytics]

    %% Student interactions
    STUDENT -->|Submits| STD_PLACEMENT
    STUDENT -->|Submits| LOGBOOK[Weekly Logbooks]
    STUDENT -->|Records| ATTENDANCE[Daily Attendance<br/>Check-in/out]
    STUDENT -->|Uploads| COMPLIANCE
    STUDENT -->|Submits| TECH_REPORT

    %% Academic Supervisor interactions
    ACAD_SUP -->|Reviews / Approves| LOGBOOK
    ACAD_SUP -->|Schedules / Conducts| VISITS
    ACAD_SUP -->|Assesses| STUDENT
    ACAD_SUP -->|Approves| ATTENDANCE

    %% Industrial Supervisor interactions
    IND_SUP -->|Reviews / Scores| LOGBOOK
    IND_SUP -->|Assesses| STUDENT
    IND_SUP -->|Approves| ATTENDANCE

    %% Cross-cutting
    NOTIF([Notification Engine]) -.- ADMIN
    NOTIF -.- COORD
    NOTIF -.- STUDENT
    NOTIF -.- ACAD_SUP
    NOTIF -.- IND_SUP

    classDef default fill:none,stroke:#000,stroke-width:1px,font-weight:bold